{"name":"Vampiric Rune","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/runes/weapon-property-runes/weapon-property-runes.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Weapons with vampiric runes are said to steal the life force out from their victims to empower their wielders. When you hit a living creature with a vampiric weapon, you gain temporary Hit Points equal to 4 + the number of damage dice your weapon deals. Double this amount on a critical hit. These temporary Hit Points last for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Tainted Virtue: The Blackguard"},"traits":{"value":["magical","necromancy"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.788,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-09-18T20:21:26.690-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.285","system":"4.0.6"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":360}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"etched-onto-a-weapon"},"level":{"value":7}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.0.6","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1663557686703,"modifiedTime":1663558106985,"lastModifiedBy":"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD"},"_id":"4f89OEPhKMNKMcSC","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3}}
{"name":"Defending Rune (Major)","type":"equipment","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/runes/weapon-property-runes/weapon-property-runes.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your weapon bears a spirit which seeks to aid in your defense. Your weapon gains the parry trait. If the weapon already had the parry trait, then the circumstance bonus to AC from parry increases to +2.</p>\n<p>When you use an Interact action to gain a circumstance bonus to AC from your weapon&rsquo;s parry trait, you can grant the circumstance bonus to an ally within 15 feet instead of gaining it yourself. You can use multiple Interact actions to protect multiple allies, or to protect yourself and an ally.</p>\n<p>While wielding this weapon, you gain the quickened condition,<br>but you can use the additional action granted only to Interact to<br>gain the benefits of the parry trait.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Special</strong> Add this option to the runes available to champions who gain the Radiant Blade Master class feat.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Tainted Virtue: The Blackguard"},"traits":{"value":["abjuration","magical"],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.788,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-09-18T20:13:26.440-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.285","system":"4.0.6"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":null,"hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{"gp":15000}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":null},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":null},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Object","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/adventuring_gear.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}},"misidentified":{}},"usage":{"value":"etched-onto-a-weapon"},"level":{"value":17}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_st