{"name":"Seal the Sanctified","type":"spell","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/spells/circle-of-protection.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can bind the powers of blessed and sacred armaments and implements within their physical forms such that they bring you no harm. You can perform a ritual and target an item with the good trait that is less than twice the level of this ritual. Its abilities and aura, aligned and magical, become suppressed. If the item has a clause or special power that would harm you for not being good-aligned or for being evil-aligned, this is also suppressed. Fundamental runes etched into armor or weapons continue to function, but property runes and abilities which require activation cannot be used. This ritual has no effect on artifacts or relics.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Critical Success </strong>Seal the sanctified succeeds, and it lasts for 10 years instead of 1.<br><strong>Success </strong>Seal the sanctified succeeds.<br><strong>Failure </strong>Seal the sanctified fails.<br><strong>Critical Failure </strong>Seal the sanctified fails spectacularly and angers good deities, who sends a sign of displeasure. For at least 1 year, further attempts to seal the sanctified the item fail.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Tainted Virtue: The Blackguard"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"uncommon","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.788,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-09-18T20:22:59.950-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.285","system":"4.0.6"}}},"level":{"value":4},"spellType":{"value":"attack"},"category":{"value":"ritual"},"traditions":{"value":[]},"school":{"value":"abjuration"},"components":{"focus":false,"material":false,"somatic":false,"verbal":false},"materials":{"value":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":""},"area":{"value":"","areaType":""},"time":{"value":"4 hours"},"duration":{"value":"1 year, or until the item is wielded by a good aligned creature"},"damage":{"value":{}},"save":{"value":"","basic":""},"sustained":{"value":false},"cost":{"value":"dark texts and unholy anointments worth a total value of 50 gp x the target's level"},"ability":{"value":""},"location":{"value":""},"hasCounteractCheck":{"value":false},"primarycheck":{"value":"Arcana, Nature, Religion, or Occultism (expert)"},"secondarycheck":{"value":""},"secondarycasters":{"value":""}},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.0.6","coreVersion":"10.285","createdTime":1663557779960,"modifiedTime":1663558106984,"lastModifiedBy":"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD"},"_id":"l1YQVKA2M1RtmMuZ","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"U618T5YHQPQrR1QD":3}}
{"name":"Unholy Reaver","type":"weapon","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/equipment/weapons/specific-magic-weapons/lifes-last-breath.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>The obsidian-black unholy reaver is the iconic weapon of powerful antipaladins and other evil ne&rsquo;er-do-wells. The crossbar of this +2 greater-striking unholy adamantine bastard-sword is styled to look like leathery bat wings, like those typically adorning powerful demons and devils. Sometimes the crossbars are instead styled to look like blackened angel wings, suggesting corruption or a fall from grace. If you are good, you are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} while carrying or wielding this weapon.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Activate </strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> command, interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Effect </strong>You command the sword and point it at a creature you can see. The sword casts @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.QnTtGCAvdWRU4spv]{Detect Alignment}, but this targets only the selected creature instead of detecting in an area.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Evil Tenets Champion Wielder</strong> If you are a champion following the tenets of evil, you also gain the following benefits.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When you critically hit a good creature with the unholy reaver, the creature becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed} 1 for 1 round.</li>\n<li>You can also activate the sword in the following way provided you are also a champion of the noted cause:</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>(Tyrant) Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> command;</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You hit a creature using the unholy reaver on your previous action</p>\n<p><strong>Effect </strong>You strip the vision away from your foe, leaving them at your mercy. You cast @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Yk3t4ekEiFIoEz9c]{Power Word Blind} as a champion spell. The spell is heightened to a spell level equal to half your level rounded up.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>(Desecrator) Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> command;</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You hit a creature using the unholy reaver on your previous action</p>\n<p><strong>Effect </strong>You instill the seeds of doubt into your foe, leaving them at war with themself. You cast @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.8kJbiBEjMWG4VUjs]{Warp Mind} as a champion spell. The spell is heightened to a spell level equal to half your level rounded up.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>(Antipaladin) Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> command</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency </strong>once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements </strong>You hit a creature using the unholy reaver on your previous action</p>\n<p><strong> Effect </strong>You further your awful destructive cause, spilling your blood and making your foe spill even more. You take [[/r 5d6]] damage, and the creature you hit takes twice the damage you received as negative or evil damage.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Tainted Virtue: The Blackguard"},"traits":{"value":["divine","evil","evocation","magical","two-hand-d12"],"rarity":"rare","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.788,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-09-18T19:49:54.651-07:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"10.285","system":"4.0.6"}}},"quantity":1,"baseItem":"bastard-sword","hp":{"brokenThreshold":0,"value":0,"max":0},"hardness":0,"weight":{"value":"-"},"equippedBulk":{"value":""},"price":{"value":{}},"equipped":{"carryType":"worn","invested":null,"handsHeld":0},"stackGroup":null,"negateBulk":{"value":"0"},"containerId":null,"preciousMaterial":{"value":"adamantine"},"preciousMaterialGrade":{"value":"standard"},"size":"med","identification":{"status":"identified","unidentified":{"name":"Unusual Weapon","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/unidentified_item_icons/weapon.webp","data":{"description":{"value":""}}}